description: Trivia game asking questions about the TV show Land of the Lost.  The game is played by asking 5 questions.  Each correct answer is worth 1 point.  The game will present 4 multiple choice answers.  You answer the question by speaking the number of the correct answer.  Then your the game will tell you if you got the correct answer and will tell you your current score.
exampleInteractions: Alexa Ask sleestak trivia to begin new game
Alexa Ask sleestak trivia to start a game
